Note: Test basic import functionality

Import "math_helpers.runa" as MathHelpers

Process called "main" takes argc as Integer, argv as Pointer returns Integer:
    Let result1 be add(5, 3)
    Display "5 + 3 = "
    Display result1
    Display "\n"

    Let result2 be multiply(4, 6)
    Display "4 * 6 = "
    Display result2
    Display "\n"

    Let result3 be square(7)
    Display "7^2 = "
    Display result3
    Display "\n"

    Return 0
End Process
